---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Games | HALM Community">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Community Games</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Connect through play and friendly competition with our community game events.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Games are a wonderful way to build relationships, stimulate the mind, and simply have fun. At HALM, we host various game nights and activities that encourage interaction among community members in a relaxed, enjoyable setting.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Regular Game Activities</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-4">
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Board Game Nights</h3>
          <p>Every Tuesday | 7:00 PM - 10:00 PM</p>
          <p class="mt-2">From strategy games to party favorites, our collection has something for everyone.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Outdoor Games</h3>
          <p>Saturdays | 4:00 PM - 6:00 PM</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Weather-permitting outdoor activities in our garden space.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card p-6 shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Trivia Nights</h3>
          <p>Last Thursday of each month | 7:30 PM</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Test your knowledge and learn something new in our themed trivia competitions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Game Library</h2>
      <p>HALM members have access to our extensive game library for use during community hours.</p>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/community/memberships" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Learn About Membership</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
